01:11:47.916 --> 01:11:48.791
<i>[children giggle]</i>

1231
01:11:48.875 --> 01:11:51.208
<i>[Tom] ♪</i> That our unanimous attitude <i>♪</i>

1232
01:11:52.375 --> 01:11:54.750
<i>♪</i> Is one of lasting gratitude <i>♪</i>

1233
01:11:55.250 --> 01:11:58.000
<i>♪</i> For what our friend
